PORT ELIZABETH - The Democratic Alliance (DA) held a rally in support of Nelson Mandela Bay (NMB) mayor Athol Trollip. That's ahead of an Economic Freedom Fighters (EFF) rally set for Wednesday afternoon aimed at gaining support to remove him from power. READ: Battle for NMB: PA throws support behind Athol Trollip The EFF vowed to punish Trollip for his party’s stance on land expropriation without compensation. The Patriotic Alliance says it will help save Trollip, only if the party’s Marlon Daniels becomes deputy mayor. eNCA